snippet.title: Fidel Dungeon Rescue - Trailer - 2018
snippet.description:
STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/573170
iOS: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/fidel-dungeon-rescue/id1383006831
ITCH: https://danielben.itch.io/fidel-dungeon-rescue

Fidel is a puzzle-crawler about finding the best path through monsters, treasure and magic. Each match is just a few minutes long, but there are many surprises and tricks to learn each time. 

============ ▼・ᴥ・▼ ============

Follow us for updates on Fidel and pics of fat dogs!
https://twitter.com/danielben
